{"tid":1681492,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"感恩節向美國領事送上愛與紙火雞","createTime":"2019-10-29T12:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T12:54:42.000Z","uid":305299,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d65cabc30839d16cc65ea0cc9e676e6be3dd9c8","tid":1681492,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:47:05.000Z","msg":"感恩節係美國超大嘅節日，係家家戶戶都會慶祝 (唔計一啲印第安部落權益等人士)，其實有無可能香港人趁機做啲野 ? 例如係遮打花園集會之後，行上美國領事，放低我地嘅留言或者心意卡，又或者再應節啲，摺埋紙火雞? 重點係吸引國際傳媒報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假如到時《香港人權法》仲未通過，啲心意卡留言內容當然就係：祝福 + 多謝一直為香港發聲 + <span style=\"color: red;\">順帶</span>爭取通過法案<br />\n<br />\n而如果《香港人權法》有幸已經通過咗，內容就可以係：祝福 + 多謝一直為香港發聲 + <span style=\"color: red;\">順帶</span>提名制裁人士<br />\n<br />\n如果依個建議係搞得過嘅話，其實有一個大問題，就係幾時搞。美國感恩節係每年11月入面第四個禮拜四，今年係11月28號，時間上香港比較難搞大型活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果正日中午搞，好處係警察放 TG 嘅機會可能細啲，壞處係人數相對少<br />\n<br />\n如果正日晚上搞，好處係人數相對會多返啲，壞處係會阻到領事自己慶祝，因為對美國人來講真係大節，係當日領事館應該會全日休息慶祝，而且感恩節晚餐對美國人真係好緊要 (有少少似我地團年飯)<br />\n<br />\n如果係提前喺週末搞嘅話，就可能要提前成一到兩個禮拜搞，因為24號係區議會選舉日，而16同17號侵侵會同維尼甚至777係智利APEC峰會見面 (777仲可能會代表香港去)，而傳媒應該會比較集中報導中美貿易協議，而9號又係柏林圍牆30週年集會，即係得返10號可能相對比較合適，大家認為呢? 如果係提前搞，個名可以考慮叫做 Early Thanksgiving Appreciation Rally (提前感恩節感謝集會)<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果大家認為搞得過，有無機會搵到人幫手申請不反對通知書，因為美國暗示過想和理非出現比例多啲<br />\n(希望可以得到大家支持，推上日程表)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====摺紙火雞 YouTube 教學傳送門=====<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uESXKf1tkwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuESXKf1tkwY&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=504f6ffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uESXKf1tkwY</a><br />\n=====2019 APEC 峰會=====<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/APEC_Chile_2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAPEC_Chile_2019&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=0227a2cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/APEC_Chile_2019</a>"},{"pid":"b4fbe4a67782e3222fcb7e6eddcc5a39f739f139","tid":1681492,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5799832f0962127232cacc6de20e5682d7c0555d","tid":1681492,"uid":86833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"咁撚左膠都畀你諗到<br />\n利申：OK"},{"pid":"73d71fee127503f8508620b55ce06016475efa35","tid":1681492,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"隻火雞好搞笑"},{"pid":"3f17439565967fb8aee9c00ae0b4b9c6841ae06d","tid":1681492,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:54:01.000Z","msg":"Good idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70287aff5ad8dbd37d96424941e857d45a514c7","tid":1681492,"uid":39840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}